DESCRIPTION
       This module retrieves the 1 minute, 5 minute, and 15
       minute load average of a machine.

SYNOPSIS
        use Sys::CpuLoad;
        print '1 min, 5 min, 15 min load average: ',
              join(',', Sys::CpuLoad::load()), "\n";


TO-DO
       Win32 support

